T02TD2633E:168a-1: sarba durga ti pa ri sho dha na ma ra ho ma bidhi ka rma kra ma /
T02TD2633E:168a-3: ngan song thams cad yongs su sbyong ba'i shi ba'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga'i las kyi rim pa /
T02TD2633E:168a-4: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
T02TD2633E:168a-5: ngan song thams cad yongs su sbyong ba gzi brjid kyi rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2633E:168a-6: gang zhig dam tshig la brtan par gnas shing /
T02TD2633E:168a-7: bla ma dang rje btsun la dbang tshul bzhin du thob pa /
T02TD2633E:168a-9: cho ga'i bye brag la mkhas pa /
T02TD2633E:168a-10: bdag dang gzhan gyi don bsgrub pa la brtson pa des /
T02TD2633E:168a-11: byams pa dang snying rje'i sems kyis /
T02TD2633E:168a-12: sems can gang dag shi ba'i dus byas te mi dge ba'i rnam par smin pas ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal myong bar 'gyur ba dang /
T02TD2633E:168a-13: nyam nga ba'i gnas nas 'don cing /
T02TD2633E:168a-14: mtho ris kyi bde ba la dgod par bya ba'i phyir /
T02TD2633E:168a-15: ngan song rnam par sbyong ba'i brtag pa las byung ba'i shi ba'i cho ga bya bar 'os so //
T02TD2633E:168a-17: bum pa tshul bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa la /
T02TD2633E:168a-18: sems can tshe 'das pa de'i ming dang sngags su sbel [*spel?] zhing /
T02TD2633E:168a-20: brgya phrag stong du tshang ba'am /
T02TD2633E:168a-21: bye ba'i tshad du bzlas na lha'i gnas su skye bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2633E:168a-22: de ni sngon du bsnyen pa'i cho ga'o /
T02TD2633E:168a-24: // / de nas sa'i cho ga bya ba ni /
T02TD2633E:168a-25: sa sngon du sbyangs pa'i gnyug ma 'am /
T02TD2633E:168b-0: der ni sa'i cho ga @168b phye mi dgos so //
T02TD2633E:168b-1: de lta bu'i gnas ma rnyed na /
T02TD2633E:168b-2: sa'i phyogs brtags par sa'i cho ga gzhung bzhin du byas la /
T02TD2633E:168b-3: dkyil 'khor ngos gcig la khru drug pa gru bzhi 'phang du khru gang ba gcig byas pa'i dbus su /
T02TD2633E:168b-4: me thab khor khor yug tu khru bzhi pa zlum po /
T02TD2633E:168b-5: zabs su khru do pa gcig bya ste ;
T02TD2633E:168b-6: mu ran 'phang dang zheng sor brgyad pa zlum por bskor /
T02TD2633E:168b-7: lci bas skyang nul legs par byas /
T02TD2633E:168b-8: sa dkar pos bsku zhing dris byugs /
T02TD2633E:168b-9: de nas thig skud thogs pa zhig gis /
T02TD2633E:168b-10: thab khung gi nang re mig dgu ru gdab /
T02TD2633E:168b-11: de nas rdo rje ra ba'i sa bcad /
T02TD2633E:168b-12: thab khung gi phyi rol du 'khor lo rtsibs bcu drug par gdab /
T02TD2633E:168b-13: de'i phyi rol du gru chad bya /
T02TD2633E:168b-14: de'i phyi rol du snam bu gnyis bya /
T02TD2633E:168b-15: de nas sgo byang nas tshon 'bras kha dog legs par bsgyur ba /
T02TD2633E:168b-16: tshon phyogs dang mdun du snod gtsang ma dris bsgos pa bsogs la /
T02TD2633E:168b-17: de mi dmigs pa las yi ge lnga las byung ba'i sa tshon bsams la /
T02TD2633E:168b-18: ye shes kyi tshon bkug la bstims la tshon phye sna lngas bri ba ni /
T02TD2633E:168b-19: me thab kyi re mig gi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa dgod /
T02TD2633E:168b-20: shar du rdo rje lhor rin po che /
T02TD2633E:168b-21: nub tu padma byad du sna tshogs rdo rje rnams rim bzhin du dgod do //
T02TD2633E:168b-22: mu ran rdo rje rkyang pa rtse lnga bas bskor /
T02TD2633E:168b-23: de'i phyi rim gyi 'khor lo rtsibs bcu drug pa /
T02TD2633E:168b-28: mgu bar ston pa rnams dgod /
T02TD2633E:168b-30: nor bu rin po che dang /
T02TD2633E:168b-32: yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i rgyal mtshan dang /
T02TD2633E:168b-34: nub kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la /
T02TD2633E:168b-39: byang gi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la /
T02TD2633E:168b-40: rdo rje kha bzhi pa dang /
T02TD2633E:168b-43: rdo rje khu tshur bcings pa rnams dgod /
T02TD2633E:168b-44: de'i phyi rim gyi gru chad kyi shar lhor /
T02TD2633E:168b-47: lho nub tu rin po che'i phreng ba dang /
T02TD2633E:168b-48: me tog / nub byang du yid du 'ong ba'i glu dang mar me /
T02TD2633E:168b-49: byang shar du gar byed pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
T02TD2633E:169a-2: shar du rdo rje gdengs pa dang zla ba /
T02TD2633E:169a-5: lho nub tu ral gri / nub tu zhags pa dang /
T02TD2633E:169a-9: byang shar du mdung rtse gsum pa rnams dgod do //
T02TD2633E:169a-10: de'i phyi rim gyi snam bu gnyis pa la /
T02TD2633E:169a-13: thig ler byas nas dgod pa ni /
T02TD2633E:169a-16: mig dmar gnyis kyi bar du rim bzhin du /
T02TD2633E:169a-21: lho'i snam bu la rim bzhin du /
T02TD2633E:169a-23: nyi ma gnyis kyi bar du /
T02TD2633E:169a-31: nub kyi snam bu la rim bzhin du /
T02TD2633E:169a-32: zla ba dang sgra gcan gnyis kyi bar du rim bzhin du /
T02TD2633E:169a-44: mon gru / mon gre / khrums stod /
T02TD2633E:169a-48: de'i phyi rim gyi snam bu la /
T02TD2633E:169a-49: sgo bzhi'i shar du lcags kyu /
T02TD2633E:169a-51: nub tu lcags sgrog / byang du khu tshur bcangs pa rnams dgod do //
T02TD2633E:169a-52: gzhan yang dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan them skas bzhi'i phreng ba dang /
T02TD2633E:169a-59: ban glang la sogs pas brgyan par bri'o //
T02TD2633E:169a-60: de ltar sbyin sreg gi dkyil 'khor bris nas /
T02TD2633E:169a-61: bum pa'am bya chus bkang ba /
T02TD2633E:169a-63: sa las byas pa'i bum pa /
T02TD2633E:169a-72: shve ta par dzi ta ste sman rnams dang /
T02TD2633E:169a-81: rin po che thams cad dang /
T02TD2633E:169a-83: bum pa'i kha rgyan la sogs pa gzhung dang mthun par byas la /
T02TD2633E:169a-84: lnga yan chad dgod pa dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-0: lha bshos snod gtsang @169b ma bkang ba brgyad dam /
T02TD2633E:169b-1: bcu drug snyed kyi bza' ba dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-7: mar me la sogs pa'i mchod pa rnams dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-8: me tog gi phreng ba rnams dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-13: 'phan la sogs pas brgyan pa dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-14: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha'am me tog gi sil ma bkram zhing ku shas bskor /
T02TD2633E:169b-15: mchod yon gyi gtor ma rgyas pa cha gnyis kyang bsham mo //
T02TD2633E:169b-16: gzhan yang sbyin sreg gi yo byad mar khu dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-25: dri zhim pa las byas pa'i sor brgyad dam /
T02TD2633E:169b-26: sor nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i bar dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-27: bud shing 'o ma can skam po zlum pa rnams dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-29: gur kum la sogs pa'i dri zhim po dag gis bskus shing byugs pa rnams bsag go //
T02TD2633E:169b-30: de ltar mchod pa'i yo byad rnams bsog go //
T02TD2633E:169b-31: bdag nyid lha'i rnal 'byor du byas nas /
T02TD2633E:169b-32: dkyil 'khor gyi yo byad rnams la /
T02TD2633E:169b-33: las thams cad pa rdo rje gnod sbyin nas /
T02TD2633E:169b-34: rdo rje rtse mo'i sngags kyis gdab /
T02TD2633E:169b-35: sreg rdzas kun la ngan song spyod ba'i sngags brgya phrag du ma bzlas shing byin gyis brlabs /
T02TD2633E:169b-36: yang na rdzas rang rang gi sngags kyis byin gyis brlab /
T02TD2633E:169b-37: de nas las thams cad pa'am /
T02TD2633E:169b-38: 'phags pa mi g-yo bas bgegs bskrad cing mtshams bcad /
T02TD2633E:169b-39: de nas bdag nyid lhar byas te dbang bskur ba dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-40: lus bsrung ba la sogs pa byas te /
T02TD2633E:169b-41: bdag nyid kyi thugs ka nas sngags brjod pas /
T02TD2633E:169b-42: phyogs phyogs kyi bgegs rnams khro bo'i skur gyur pas bsrung bar bsam pa ni /
T02TD2633E:169b-43: steng du rdo rje 'jigs byed kyis bsrung /
T02TD2633E:169b-44: shar du rdo rje gtsug tor dang /
T02TD2633E:169b-46: nub tu rdo rje ba dan gyis bsrung /
T02TD2633E:169b-47: lhor rdo rje rtse mos bsrung /
T02TD2633E:169b-48: byang du rdo rje nag pos bsrung /
T02TD2633E:169b-49: mtshams bzhir 'jigs byed spyan gyis bsrung /
T02TD2633E:169b-50: 'og rdo rje gnod sbyin gyis bsrung /
T02TD2633E:169b-51: steng pam las rdo rje ra ba bya /
T02TD2633E:169b-52: badzra karmas rdo rje lnga pa'i ba bya /
T02TD2633E:169b-53: phur bus snga nas gnas pa bskrad /
T02TD2633E:170a-3: de nas bdag nyid kyi snying gar sna tshogs rdo rje a'a las bsams la /
T02TD2633E:170a-4: rdo rje bsdu bas 'phags pa rnams spyan drangs te /
T02TD2633E:170a-5: phyag rgya bzhis bzhugs su gsol la /
T02TD2633E:170a-6: yon chab la sogs pa mchod pa rnams tshul bzhin du dbul lo //
T02TD2633E:170a-7: de nas gtor ma rnams tshul bzhin du byin gyis brlabs nas /
T02TD2633E:170a-8: dam tshig can rnams la gtor ma phul te /
T02TD2633E:170a-9: ming 'di zhes bya ba'i sgrib pa byang zhing /
T02TD2633E:170a-10: bdag 'gro ba'i don brtson pa'i stong grogs mdzad du gsol zhes brjod do //
T02TD2633E:170a-11: 'gro ba spyir gtor ma bsngos nas ;
T02TD2633E:170a-12: ming 'di zhes bya ba'i lan chags byang zhing /
T02TD2633E:170a-13: bsod nams kyi tshogs su gyur cig ces brjod de gtang /
T02TD2633E:170a-14: de nas sngags mkhan gzhan zhig yod na /
T02TD2633E:170a-15: bum pa la rigs lnga'i snying po dang /
T02TD2633E:170a-16: shi ba'i ming spel zhing cung zad bzlas la /
T02TD2633E:170a-17: de nas ngan song sbyong ba'i sngags ci mang du bzlas brjod bya'o //
T02TD2633E:170a-18: gzhan med na bdag nyid kyis bum pa gcig la /
T02TD2633E:170a-19: ngan song sbyong ba'i sngags ci nus kyis bzlas so //
T02TD2633E:170a-20: de nas bud shing la ngan song sbyong ba'i sngags kyis btab ste brtsig pa ni /
T02TD2633E:170a-21: shing drang zhing dri dang ldan na legs /
T02TD2633E:170a-22: dri med kyang shing drang zhing ring ba'i gdung /
T02TD2633E:170a-23: ka ba bzhi thab kyi zur bzhi ru btsugs pa'i steng du /
T02TD2633E:170a-25: phyi ma de gnyis kyi steng du phyam them par dgod /
T02TD2633E:170a-26: de nas steng du rtsibs brtsigs la /
T02TD2633E:170a-27: steng khang sum rim byas la /
T02TD2633E:170a-28: mchod rten gyi tshul du brtsigs /
T02TD2633E:170a-30: steng non ro bzhag la brtsig par bya'o /
T02TD2633E:170a-32: // / de nas bdag nyid lha'i rnal 'byor du byas te /
T02TD2633E:170a-33: shi ba'i lus la gnas pa dang /
T02TD2633E:170a-34: khog bsrungs la sogs pa'i bar du gcod pa'i bgegs bskrad pa ni /
T02TD2633E:170a-35: rdo rje gsor zhing na mo badzra satva kro dha aa na l'arka ma h'a badzra kro dha /
T02TD2633E:170a-37: bi dra ba bi dra ba /
T02TD2633E:170a-39: n'a sha ya n'a sha ya /
T02TD2633E:170a-43: de nas lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
T02TD2633E:170a-44: aom badzra aam ku sha che ge mo dza:/
T02TD2633E:170a-46: tshe 'das pa de gang na gnas kyang rung ste /
T02TD2633E:170b-0: rang dbang med par lcags kyu can @170b gyis bkug par bsam /
T02TD2633E:170b-1: aom badzra p'a sha h'um gis ro la gshegs pa gzhug / aom badzra spho ta bam gyis bsdams /
T02TD2633E:170b-3: sems ma 'khrugs par dga' bar bya /
T02TD2633E:170b-4: de nas ro la ngan song sbyong ba'i sngags kyis btab la /
T02TD2633E:170b-5: sngon du bzlas pa'i bum pa'i chus bkru / bkrus pa dang kun gzhi'i las dang /
T02TD2633E:170b-6: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags gangs kyi rim pa bzhin du gnas pa dag par bsam /
T02TD2633E:170b-7: de nas sngags bzlas shing dris byug /
T02TD2633E:170b-8: de nas sngags kyis btab pa'i ras dkar po kha tshar ma nyams pas dkri /
T02TD2633E:170b-9: sngags kyis btab pa'i bdug pas bdug / me tog gi phreng bas kyang ro la gdags so //
T02TD2633E:170b-10: de ni ro la sngags gdags shing byin gyis brlab ste /
T02TD2633E:170b-11: gur kum bzang pos bri ba ni /
T02TD2633E:170b-12: aom bri ta bri ta sarba a'a ba ra na ni h'um phat /
T02TD2633E:170b-13: lus kyi spyi bor gdags so //
T02TD2633E:170b-14: aom tra ta tra ta sarba a'a pa ra na ni h'um phat /
T02TD2633E:170b-15: ngag ste mgrin pa'i lce rtsar gdags so //
T02TD2633E:170b-16: aom tshindha tshindha sarba a'a ba ra na ni h'um phat /
T02TD2633E:170b-17: yid de snying gar gdags te /
T02TD2633E:170b-18: lus ngag yid gsum gyi mi dge ba bcu'i bag chags dag par dmigs so //
T02TD2633E:170b-19: da ni gnas bco brgyad du gdags te /
T02TD2633E:170b-20: aom sho dha ni sho dha ni sarba aa p'a ya bi sho dha ni sarba karma a'a pa ra na bi shuddhe bi shuddhe /
T02TD2633E:170b-21: kun rig gi ste dbu la'o //
T02TD2633E:170b-22: aom sho dha ni sho dha ya sarba aa p'a ya bi sho dha ni stha h'um phat /
T02TD2633E:170b-23: ngan song sbyong ba'i ste mdzod spu la'o //
T02TD2633E:170b-24: aom sho dha ni sho dha ni sarba aa p'a ya sa tve bhya h'um tr'am /
T02TD2633E:170b-25: rin chen tog gi ste rna ba g-yas pa la'o //
T02TD2633E:170b-26: aom sho dha ni sho dha ya sarba aa p'a ya bi sho dha ni hr'i:/
T02TD2633E:170b-27: sh'akya thub pa'i ste rna ba g-yon pa la'o //
T02TD2633E:170b-28: aom sho dha ni sho dha ya sarba aa p'a ya tra ta aa /
T02TD2633E:170b-29: me tog che rgyas kyi ste mgo bo'i gtsug phud la'o //
T02TD2633E:170b-30: na mo bha ga ba te sarba durga ti pa ri sho dha na r'a dz'a ye /
T02TD2633E:170b-31: ta th'a ga t'a ya aarha te /
T02TD2633E:170b-34: aom sho dha ni sho dha ni sarba p'a pam bi sho dha ni /
T02TD2633E:170b-35: shuddhe bi shuddhe sarba karma a'a ba ra na bi shodha ni sv'a h'a /
T02TD2633E:170b-36: rtsa ba'i rig pa ste dpung pa g-yas pa la'o //
T02TD2633E:170b-37: aom sarba bti sarba a'a ba ra na bi sho dha ni ha na h'um phat /
T02TD2633E:171a-16: gsang ba'i gnas te mdoms su gdags pa ste /
T02TD2633E:171a-17: de bzhin yid kyis kyang sngags rnams dgod do //
T02TD2633E:171a-18: de dag gi 'od zer gyis sgrib pa rnams byang bar bsam mo //
T02TD2633E:171a-19: de nas sngags kyis btab pa'i der la sogs pa'i gos kyis g-yogs nas ;
T02TD2633E:171a-21: stan padma 'dab ma brgyad dang bcas par bzhag ste /
T02TD2633E:171a-22: kha nub tu bstan la gzhag go //
T02TD2633E:171a-23: sngags mkhan bdag nyid kha shar phyogs su bltas la las bya'o //
T02TD2633E:171a-24: de nas bzlas pa las kyi bum chus /
T02TD2633E:171a-25: thab dang sreg rdzas la sogs pa thams cad rnam par bsangs te /
T02TD2633E:171a-26: shin tu gtsang ba'i rtsva ku sha'i khres la /
T02TD2633E:171a-27: bkra shis kyi skyil mo krung gis 'dug ste /
T02TD2633E:171a-28: chos thams cad stong pa nyid du bsgom mo //
T02TD2633E:171a-29: stong pa'i khyad par las yi ge aa thung dur gyur te /
T02TD2633E:171a-31: de 'od du zhu ba las dam tshig gi phyag rgya rdo rje /
T02TD2633E:171a-32: rdo rje de'i lte ba yang h'um bsams te /
T02TD2633E:171a-34: sku gsung thugs kyi dbyings gang /
T02TD2633E:171a-35: thams cad bkug ste 'od du zhu ba las /
T02TD2633E:171a-36: sgrub pa po bdag nyid lha'i rnal 'byor du sngags 'di brjod pas gyur par bsam mo //
T02TD2633E:171a-37: aom sho dha ni sho dha ni sarba p'a pam bi sho dha ni shuddhe bi shuddhe /
T02TD2633E:171a-38: sarba karma a'a ba ra na bi shuddhe sv'a h'a /
T02TD2633E:171a-39: 'khor lo'i phyag rgya rdo rje'i khu tshur gnyis bcings te /
T02TD2633E:171a-40: go rims kyis 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshul du dbye zhing sngags brjod pas /
T02TD2633E:171a-41: bcom ldan 'das kun rig gi rgyal po sku mdog dung dang kun da ltar dkar ba zhal bzhi pa /
T02TD2633E:171a-42: phyag gnyis ting nge 'dzin du bsnol ba /
T02TD2633E:171a-43: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa cig bskyed de /
T02TD2633E:171a-44: de nas rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'i phyag rgya ni /
T02TD2633E:171a-45: mthe bong gnyis ni skyil mo krung //
T02TD2633E:171a-46: mdzub mo gnyis ni rtse mo dgug / gung mo rtse mo mnyam pa ste //
T02TD2633E:171b-0: rdo rje dbyings kyi @171b dbang mo'o //
T02TD2633E:171b-1: sngags ni aom badzra dh'a tv'i shva ri h'um dza /
T02TD2633E:171b-2: aom badzra ni aa dhi tishth'a ya /
T02TD2633E:171b-3: zhes brjod cing snying ga dang lkog ma dang /
T02TD2633E:171b-4: smin mtshams dang spyi bor byin gyis brlab bo //
T02TD2633E:171b-5: de nas dbang bskur te rdo rje bcings pa la /
T02TD2633E:171b-6: mthe bong gnyis rtse mo can du byas te /
T02TD2633E:171b-7: de'i steng du mdzub mo gnyis phan tshun ngos sprad de /
T02TD2633E:171b-8: rin po che'i rtse mo 'dra bar byas pa ni /
T02TD2633E:171b-9: rin po che'i phyag rgya ste /
T02TD2633E:171b-10: snying po ni aom badzra ratna zhes spyi bor rin po che'i dbang bskur ro //
T02TD2633E:171b-11: de nas rang gi lce la rdo rje rtse lnga pa chos kyi phyag rgya h'um las bskyed de /
T02TD2633E:171b-12: de'i dbus su chos kyi phyag rgya sku bskyed pa'i snying po bsam mo ;
T02TD2633E:171b-13: / de nas rang gi snying gar las kyi phyag rgya rdzogs par byed pa /
T02TD2633E:171b-14: sna tshogs rdo rje rgya gram yi ge aa las bsams te /
T02TD2633E:171b-15: de'i dbus su yang aa bsam mo //
T02TD2633E:171b-16: de ltar bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i sku bskyed pa rdzogs par bskyed pa des /
T02TD2633E:171b-17: rdo rje rab dang dra ba la sogs pas bsrung pa'i 'khor lo gsal bar byas te /
T02TD2633E:171b-18: las thams cad pa'i bum chus /
T02TD2633E:171b-20: zhes bya bas rdzas thams cad bsangs te /
T02TD2633E:171b-21: de nas dngul gyi snod du mchod yon gyi chu dri zhim po'i nang du /
T02TD2633E:171b-24: 'bru sna tshogs blugs te g-yon du gzhag / mchod pa lnga g-yon du gzhag / rdo rje dril bu g-yon du gzhag / sreg rdzas dang yo byad la sogs pa g-yas su gzhag / mar bzhu ba dang dgang gzar blugs gzar mdun du gzhag / rdzas gzhag pa'i rim pa'o /

T02TD2633E:175a-26: drang bor bcas pa chags pa'o //
T02TD2633E:175a-27: sarba bid badzra r'a ga ho//
T02TD2633E:175a-28: de las mdzub gnyis slar bkug ste //
T02TD2633E:175a-29: se gol gtogs pa legs pa'o //
T02TD2633E:175a-30: sarba bid badzra sv'a dhu dhu /
T02TD2633E:175a-31: de las bar ma tshigs bcag pa //
T02TD2633E:175a-32: rdo rje rin chen yin pa'o //
T02TD2633E:175a-34: de las sor mo 'od zer ltar //
T02TD2633E:175a-35: bkyed pa rdo rje gzi brjid do //
T02TD2633E:175a-37: de las spyi bor bzhag pa ni //
T02TD2633E:175a-38: rdo rje rgyal mtshan phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2633E:175a-40: de las phab nas kha ru ni //
T02TD2633E:175a-41: bzhag ba rdo rje bzhad pa'o //
T02TD2633E:175a-43: bcings las mdzub gnyis pa de ltar bya //
T02TD2633E:175a-44: rdo rje chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2633E:175a-46: mdzub gnyis dad po tshigs bcag pa //
T02TD2633E:175a-49: mdzub gnyis gdu bu ltar byas pa //
T02TD2633E:175a-51: sarba bid krum / de las mdzub gnyis padma yi //
T02TD2633E:175a-54: de las mdzub gnyis dgye byas pa //
T02TD2633E:175a-55: las kyi rdo rje phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2633E:175a-56: sarba bid kam / de las mdzub gnyis rab bkye ste //
T02TD2633E:175a-59: de las rtse mo slar bkug ste //
T02TD2633E:175a-60: mche ba ltar byas gnod sbyin no //
T02TD2633E:175a-61: sarba bid kasham / de nas mdzub gnyis nang bsdus te //
T02TD2633E:175a-62: rab tu bsdams pas khu tshur ro //
T02TD2633E:175b-0: @175b rdo rje bsdams pa dam byas te //
T02TD2633E:175b-1: mthe bong gnyis gshibs l'a sye'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-2: aom sarba bid ma h'a badzrod bh'a ba d'a na p'a ra mi t'a p'u dza h'um /
T02TD2633E:175b-3: de nas kha nas mdun du ni //
T02TD2633E:175b-4: lag pa brkyang ba m'a le'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-5: aom sarba bid ma h'a badzrod bh'a ba sh'i la p'a ra mi t'a p'u dza tram /
T02TD2633E:175b-6: thal mo sbyar ba m'a le nas //
T02TD2633E:175b-7: phar drangs pa ni k'i rti'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-8: aom sarba bid ma h'a badzrod bh'a wa ksh'an ti p'a ra mi t'a p'u dza hr'i:/
T02TD2633E:175b-9: gar las rdo rje thal mo ni //
T02TD2633E:175b-10: spyi bor bzhag pa na rti'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-11: aom sarba bid ma h'a badzrod bh'a ba b'i rya p'a ra mi t'a p'u dza aa:/
T02TD2633E:175b-12: bsdams pa thur blugs bdug pa'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-13: aom sarba bti sarba aa p'a ya bi sho dha na dha ma dha ma dhu pa ya dhya na p'a ra mi t'a p'u dza h'um /
T02TD2633E:175b-14: thams cad du 'thor me tog go //
T02TD2633E:175b-15: aom sarba bti sarba aa p'a ya pushpa bi lo ki ni pradzny'a na p'a ra mi t'a p'u dza tram /
T02TD2633E:175b-17: aom sarba bti sarba aa p'a ya dzny'a na aa ba lo ka ka ri pra ni dhi p'a ra mi t'a p'u dza hr'i:/
T02TD2633E:175b-18: rdo rje bsdams pa brkyang byug dri'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-19: aom sarba bti sarba aa p'a ya gandha au pa ya p'a ra mi t'a p'u dza a'a /
T02TD2633E:175b-20: mdzub gnyis bkug pa lcags kyu'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-21: aom sarba bti sarba na ra ka a'aksha ni h'um phat /
T02TD2633E:175b-22: mdzub rtse sprad pa zhags pa'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-23: aom sarba bti sarba na da ka au da ra ni h'um phat /
T02TD2633E:175b-24: mdzub gnyis 'khyud pa lcags sgrog go //
T02TD2633E:175b-25: aom sarba bti sarba na ra ka bandha mo tsa ni h'um phat /
T02TD2633E:175b-26: rab tu bkod pa'i dril bu'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-27: aom sarba bti sarba na ra ka ghante bi sho dha ni h'um phat /
T02TD2633E:175b-28: de nas las kyi phyag rgya rnams //
T02TD2633E:175b-29: mdor bsdus rab tu bshad par bya //
T02TD2633E:175b-30: g-yon pa lte bar brkyang ba la //
T02TD2633E:175b-31: g-yas pa rdo rje'i tshul du ni //
T02TD2633E:175b-32: kun rig snang mdzad phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-33: ngan song sbyong la sogs pa bzhi //
T02TD2633E:175b-34: sa gnon mchod sbyin ting nge 'dzin //
T02TD2633E:175b-35: mi 'dzin sbyin sogs go rims bzhin //
T02TD2633E:175b-37: lcags kyu g-yas kyis 'dzin pa yin //
T02TD2633E:175b-38: mda' 'phangs tshul dang se gol dang //
T02TD2633E:175b-39: mdzub bsgreng dpral khar 'dzin rin chen //
T02TD2633E:175b-40: khu tshur gshibs pa nyi ma'i 'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-41: khu tshur g-yon mdog g-yas gru gzugs //
T02TD2633E:175b-42: kha yi phyogs bzhag bzhad pa'o //
T02TD2633E:175b-43: g-yas kyis g-yon dbye chos kyi yin //
T02TD2633E:175b-44: ral gri gnyis dpung 'dzin rnon po //
T02TD2633E:175b-45: khu tshur snying gar gshibs khyod 'khor /
T02TD2633E:176a-0: @176a * // kha zad nas drangs smra ba'i rgya //
T02TD2633E:176a-1: khu tshur gnyis ni gar byas te //
T02TD2633E:176a-2: 'gram pa g-yas g-yon gzhag par bya //
T02TD2633E:176a-3: de nas yang bskor spyi bor bzhag / spyi bor bskor ba las kyi'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-4: khu tshur go cha'i tshul phyag rgya //
T02TD2633E:176a-5: de nas mthe chung mche gnod sbyin //
T02TD2633E:176a-6: khu tshur gnyis nas khu tshur rgya'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-7: de las dku gnyis g-yas g-yon du //
T02TD2633E:176a-10: kha nas ba byung tshul g'irti'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-11: gar du byas pa ni rti'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-12: de las khu tshur thur du ni //
T02TD2633E:176a-13: blugs pa ltar byas bdug pa'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-14: gyen du 'thor ba me tog go ;
T02TD2633E:176a-15: / mdun du gshibs pa mar me'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-16: khu tshur rtse sprad brang la ni //
T02TD2633E:176a-18: mthe'u chung mdzub gnyis so so ru //
T02TD2633E:176a-20: de las mdzub gnyis rtse sprad pa //
T02TD2633E:176a-21: gdu bur byas pa zhags pa'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-22: de nas gung mdzub mtheb rtse sprad ;
T02TD2633E:176a-23: / lu gu rgyud ltar byas pa las //
T02TD2633E:176a-24: lhag ma bsdus pa lcags sgrog go //
T02TD2633E:176a-25: de nas mdzub gnyis 'khyud pa las //
T02TD2633E:176a-26: khu tshur mnan bskyod dril bu'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-27: lce la padma'i zla dkyil du //
T02TD2633E:176a-28: gong du bstan pa'i sngags de dag / bkod nas zla ba bya ba de //
T02TD2633E:176a-29: chos kyi phyag rgyar rab bstan pa'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-30: ji ltar bstan pa'i bsgoms pa dang //
T02TD2633E:176a-31: phyag rgya phyag mtshan 'dzin pa dang //
T02TD2633E:176a-32: thugs kar rdo rje bsgom pa ni //
T02TD2633E:176a-33: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' yis //
T02TD2633E:176a-34: phyag rgya chen por bstan pa'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-35: 'jig rten pa yi phyag rgya ni //
T02TD2633E:176a-36: mthe bong mthe'u chung rtse sprad de //
T02TD2633E:176a-37: lhag ma gsum ni rdo rjer bya //
T02TD2633E:176a-38: de ni brgya byin phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2633E:176a-39: g-yas pa be con ltar byas pa //
T02TD2633E:176a-40: g-yon pa mgo thog ba cer byas la //
T02TD2633E:176a-42: g-yas pa zhags pa 'dzin byas te //
T02TD2633E:176a-43: g-yon pa sprul gyi gdengs kar byas //
T02TD2633E:176a-45: g-yas pa snye ma 'dzin pa dang //
T02TD2633E:176a-46: g-yon pa mdzub mo bkug pa ni //
T02TD2633E:176a-48: g-yas thal brkyang sbyar mthe bong bkug / smrang 'don lta bur byas pa dang //
T02TD2633E:176b-0: @176b g-yas pa ral gri 'dzin pa dang //
T02TD2633E:176b-1: gung mo srin lag mthil bkug pa //
T02TD2633E:176b-2: bden bral srin po'i phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2633E:176b-3: g-yas pa ba dan tshul byas nas //
T02TD2633E:176b-4: g-yon pa btsir ba'i tshul byas ni //
T02TD2633E:176b-6: g-yas pa phreng ba 'dzin pa dang //
T02TD2633E:176b-7: g-yon pa zhags mig ltar byas pa //
T02TD2633E:176b-9: thal mo mnyam par sbyar ba ni //
T02TD2633E:176b-10: pa ba sangs dang mig dmar ro //
T02TD2633E:176b-11: kha thad mdzub bsgreng phur bu'o //
T02TD2633E:176b-12: lag g-yas thal bgrad nyi ma la'o //
T02TD2633E:176b-13: zla ba g-yon pa bgrad pa'o //
T02TD2633E:176b-14: glang sna chu srin 'dra sgra gcan //
T02TD2633E:176b-15: se gol gtogs pa gza' lag ste //
T02TD2633E:176b-16: sben pa g-yon pa 'dzin ltar bya //
T02TD2633E:176b-17: lag pa gnyis kyi mkhrig ma bsnol //
T02TD2633E:176b-18: bkan te g-yas pa'i steng byung nas //
T02TD2633E:176b-19: sor mo bsdu zhing bsnol ba ste //
T02TD2633E:176b-20: rgyu skar spyi yi phyag rgya'o //
T02TD2633E:176b-21: de ltar dkyil 'khor lha rnams phyag rgyas btab nas /
T02TD2633E:176b-22: de nas zhabs bsil gyi snod blangs la //
T02TD2633E:176b-23: yid kyis zhabs bsil dbul bar bya'o //
T02TD2633E:176b-24: sngags aom pra ba ra satka ra pra t'itstsha sv'a h'a /
T02TD2633E:176b-25: de nas mchod yon lag tu dbul lo //
T02TD2633E:176b-26: ai ma aargham sa ma ya stvam /
T02TD2633E:176b-27: tri lan siddhimme pra yatstsha sv'a h'a /
T02TD2633E:176b-28: mchod yon phyag tu dbul bar bya'o //
T02TD2633E:176b-29: rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma la sogs pas dbang bskur ro //
T02TD2633E:176b-31: shin tu dri zhim pa'i me tog dang /
T02TD2633E:176b-32: aom badzra pushpe zhes bya ba dang /
T02TD2633E:176b-33: snying po dkar po'i bdug spos dang /
T02TD2633E:176b-36: ba'i mar gyi mar me dang /
T02TD2633E:176b-37: aom badzra di pe a'a lo ke / zhes bya ba dang /
T02TD2633E:176b-39: tsandan gyi dri zhim po dkar po dang /
T02TD2633E:176b-42: kha zas dkar gsum mngon par bsngags la /
T02TD2633E:176b-43: aom aa k'a ro mu kham sarba dharm'a n'am a'adya nutpannatv'ata /
T02TD2633E:176b-45: de dag dang pos bsangs te /
T02TD2633E:176b-46: so so las kyi phyag rgya dang bcas pas gtugs la byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
T02TD2633E:176b-47: de nas yang dbul ba la sogs pa'i mchod pa bya ba'i phyag rgya bzhi'o //
T02TD2633E:176b-48: de nas bdug pa la sogs pa'i las kyi phyag rgya bcings te /
T02TD2633E:176b-49: snying po brjod cing mchod pa ni /
T02TD2633E:176b-50: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis ka thur du bstan te bkrol la dbul /
T02TD2633E:177a-1: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis me tog 'thor ba'i tshul du gyen du bstan te bkrol la /
T02TD2633E:177a-4: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis mar me'i lce ltar gyen du bzung la /
T02TD2633E:177a-5: badzra a'a lo ke / zhes bya bas dbul /
T02TD2633E:177a-6: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis byug sbos byug pa'i tshul du rang gi lus la bcar te brkyang la /
T02TD2633E:177a-9: de nas yang gsang ba'i mchod pas mchod par byas te /
T02TD2633E:177a-10: las kyi phyag rgya bcing ba ni /
T02TD2633E:177a-11: rdo rje khu tshur mkhal ltag gnyis su bzhag ste /
T02TD2633E:177a-12: l'a sye'i snying po'i don sems la bsam zhing sems dang par gyur pas glo g-yon par mgo bo btud pa ni rdo rje mdzes ma'o //
T02TD2633E:177a-13: sngags aom badzra sa tva su sam gra ha dang /
T02TD2633E:177a-14: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis rang gi mgo la phreng ba bcing ba'i tshul du byas pa ni phreng ba ma'i 'o //
T02TD2633E:177a-15: sngags aom badzra ratna ma nutta ram /
T02TD2633E:177a-16: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis kha nas tshig 'byin pa ltar byas pa ni dbyangs mkhan ma'i'o //
T02TD2633E:177a-17: sngags aom badzra dharma ga ya ne /
T02TD2633E:177a-18: rdo rje khu tshur g-yon pa mdun du bkan te bzhag la //
T02TD2633E:177a-19: de'i steng du khu tshur g-yas pa kha sbub ste bzhag nas /
T02TD2633E:177a-20: ldem bag can du lag pa gnyis phan tshul dkri zhing /
T02TD2633E:177a-21: g-yon pa'i mdzub mo la sogs pa dgrol ba'i tshul du byas te /
T02TD2633E:177a-22: de bzhin du g-yas pa khu tshur la sogs dgrol ba'i tshul du byas pa ni /
T02TD2633E:177a-24: sngags aom badzra karma ka rod bh'a ba /
T02TD2633E:177a-25: da ni mchod pa nyi shus mchod par bya ste /
T02TD2633E:177a-26: 'di ni mchod pa nyi shus de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la kun du mchod nas /
T02TD2633E:177a-27: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs ka'i mtshan ma'i dbus su rang gi chos kyi phyag rgya dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid du bsams te /
T02TD2633E:177a-29: 'thor 'thung snga ma bzhin du sbyin sreg gi yo byad thams cad bsang gtor byas la /
T02TD2633E:177a-30: dgang gzar dang blugs gzar lag tu blangs la /
T02TD2633E:177a-32: mar gyis bkang ste spar zhing /
T02TD2633E:177a-33: ji snyed pa thams cad me'i zhal du bstabs par bya'o //
T02TD2633E:177a-34: de nas gtso bo la me lha nyid dbul bar bya'o //
T02TD2633E:177a-35: de nas rgyal ba lnga dang /
T02TD2633E:177b-0: sems dpa' bcu drug po rnams la brgya rtsa brgyad @177b dbul /
T02TD2633E:177b-1: lhag ma rnams la nyi shu rtsa gcig dbul lo //
T02TD2633E:177b-2: rdzas rnams ni gong du rgyas par smos bar zad do //
T02TD2633E:177b-3: de nas gong du smos pa'i rdo rje dril bu rnam pa gnyis padma'i lag skor lnga byas te /
T02TD2633E:177b-4: sangs rgyas thams cad la bstod par bya'o //
T02TD2633E:177b-5: chos nyid ye shes skyon bral ba'i //
T02TD2633E:177b-6: rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD2633E:177b-7: ting nge 'dzin ldan phyag rgya can //
T02TD2633E:177b-8: phyag 'tshal rdo rje kun rig la'o //
T02TD2633E:177b-9: me long ye shes rang bzhin las //
T02TD2633E:177b-10: sems can ma lus thams cad kyi //
T02TD2633E:177b-11: ngan song thams cad sbyong mdzad pa //
T02TD2633E:177b-12: phyag 'tshal sbyong ba'i rgyal po la //
T02TD2633E:177b-13: mnyam nyid ye shes yon tan bdag / yid bzhin nor bu rin chen gyis //
T02TD2633E:177b-14: bsam pa thams cad skong mdzad pa //
T02TD2633E:177b-15: rgyal mchog rin chen khyod phyag 'tshal //
T02TD2633E:177b-16: so sor kun rtog gsung gi bdag / gsung rab padma'i kha rgyas pa //
T02TD2633E:177b-17: khams gsum dbugs 'byin mdzad pa po //
T02TD2633E:177b-19: nan tan ye shes phrin las bdag / sna tshogs sems can sdug bsngal kun //
T02TD2633E:177b-20: ma lus sems ni zhi mdzad pa //
T02TD2633E:177b-21: me tog cher rgyas khyod phyag 'tshal //
T02TD2633E:177b-22: grva yi phyogs ni kun du yang //
T02TD2633E:177b-23: rigs kyi yum gyi sku bstan pa //
T02TD2633E:177b-24: lo tsan dang m'a ma k'i //
T02TD2633E:177b-25: dkar mo sgrol ma khyod phyag 'tshal //
T02TD2633E:177b-26: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
T02TD2633E:177b-28: phyag 'tshal rdo rje khu tshur la'o //
T02TD2633E:177b-30: sgeg mo phreng dang dbyangs dang gar //
T02TD2633E:177b-31: spos ma me tog mar me dang //
T02TD2633E:177b-32: dri chab la sogs lha mo brgyad //
T02TD2633E:177b-33: phyi nang lha mo phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2633E:177b-34: de yi phyi rim gnas pa yi //
T02TD2633E:177b-35: 'jig rten skyong ba brgyad po la //
T02TD2633E:177b-36: 'khor dang bcas pa gnas pa ni //
T02TD2633E:177b-37: mche ba drug pa mdog dkar ba'i //
T02TD2633E:177b-38: glang chen de ni brgya byin gdan //
T02TD2633E:177b-40: mtshan ma sha rtsi au pa s'i //
T02TD2633E:177b-42: lho phyogs gshin rje'i rgyal po ni //
T02TD2633E:177b-43: ma he'i gdan can g-yon dkur brten //
T02TD2633E:177b-44: mchan na nag mo 'chi bdag mo //
T02TD2633E:177b-46: nub phyogs ngos kyi chu lha ni //
T02TD2633E:177b-47: lus mdog dkar zhing 'tsher ba la //
T02TD2633E:178a-2: zhags pa rin chen bsnams phyag 'tshal //
T02TD2633E:178a-3: byang phyogs gnod sbyin rgyal po ni //
T02TD2633E:178a-4: gser gyi mdog 'dra rin chen dang //
T02TD2633E:178a-5: g-yon pa snye ma rta yi gdan //
T02TD2633E:178a-6: mchan na chung ma bsnams phyag 'tshal //
T02TD2633E:178a-7: me gzugs kha dog drug 'dra ba'i ;
T02TD2633E:178a-8: / dkyil na na chung gnas pa yi //
T02TD2633E:178a-9: lus dmar po la ra skyes gdan //
T02TD2633E:178a-11: lho nub mtshams kyi bden bral ni //
T02TD2633E:178a-12: yi dags gdan can dmar nag mdog / me bur ba ni g-yon na 'dzin //
T02TD2633E:178a-14: nub byang rlung lha'i rgyal po ni //
T02TD2633E:178a-15: nam mkha'i mdog can sha ba'i gdan //
T02TD2633E:178a-16: ba dan gyen du bsgreng ba 'dzin //
T02TD2633E:178a-17: g-yon pa rlung sgye'u thogs phyag 'tshal //
T02TD2633E:178a-18: byang shar 'byung po'i rgyal po ni //
T02TD2633E:178a-19: thal ba'i mdog 'dra rta yi gdan //
T02TD2633E:178a-20: g-yas nyid rtse gsum aa 'bra dang //
T02TD2633E:178a-21: g-yon nyid gundhe rag sha phreng //
T02TD2633E:178a-22: bgegs gdon rnams la dbang sgyur zhing //
T02TD2633E:178a-24: de yi phyi rim phyogs bzhi na //
T02TD2633E:178a-25: bar na gza' rnams brgyad gnas pa //
T02TD2633E:178a-26: pa ba sangs dang mig dmar gnyis //
T02TD2633E:178a-27: shar na gnas shing 'khor rnams skyong //
T02TD2633E:178a-28: smin drug snar ma mgo dang lag / nab so rgyal skag sogs phyag 'tshal //
T02TD2633E:178a-29: phur bu dang ni nyi ma gnyis //
T02TD2633E:178a-30: lho na gnas shing 'khor skyong ba //
T02TD2633E:178a-31: mchu dang gre dang dbo dang ni //
T02TD2633E:178a-32: me bzhi nag pa sa ri dang //
T02TD2633E:178a-33: sa ga la sogs phyag 'tshal bstod //
